title: Artistic Retro Hoodies – Stylish Three-Quarter Sleeve Fashion for Men & Women
body_html:
Embrace a bold, artistic style with this retro-inspired hoodie. Made from premium metal silk fabric, it combines comfort and eye-catching design. With a wide range of vibrant colors and a flattering three-quarter sleeve design, this hoodie is perfect for casual outings, creative activities, or just making a statement.

✨ Features:

  • Premium metal silk fabric for a unique, smooth feel
  • Artistic retro style for a distinct, fashionable look
  • Three-quarter sleeves provide a chic and relaxed fit
  • Available in a variety of vibrant colors: White, Khaki, Light Purple, Light Blue, Dark Green, Black, Pink, Red, Light Green, Yellow, Gray, and White 1
  • Hong Kong style adds a touch of uniqueness to your wardrobe
  • Sizes XS to XXXL, ensuring a great fit for a variety of body types
  • Versatile for casual wear, artistic events, or creative outfits

Package Includes:

  • 1 x Artistic Retro Hoodie

Size Options:

  • XS, S, M, L, XL, XXL, XXXL

⚠️ Note:

  •  Asian sizes are smaller than European and American sizes. Choose the larger size if you're between two sizes.
  • Allow 2-3 cm differences due to manual measurement.
  • Color may vary slightly based on monitor display settings.
